{"title":"在未到过的故乡","authors":["黎之"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":3,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在未到过的故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎之"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我陌生而又熟悉的大连港，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是我未到过的故乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我曾站在你的对岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整日向你眺望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那万顷波涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧接着我的家门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那宽广的大路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留有我亲人的脚印。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你这里人们的谈话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着浓重的我故乡的声音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在老家的门前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送走了我的祖父，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又送走了我的父亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们背负着生活的重担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向你走来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“死逼梁山下关东”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们想在这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"减轻生活的苦辛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，父亲带着祖父的骨灰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重返故乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海的波涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋葬了我们的希望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我没有见过的大连港啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你难道是个吃人的地方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时光在战斗中过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走过很多祖国的土地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大连啊，这我父辈受苦的城市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还没有见过你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是不是和祖国每个城市一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变得年轻而又美丽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列车带我向关外驰骋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面前闪动着父亲的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我早逝的父亲哪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果你和我一起重返大连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你该是多么高兴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大连像年轻的战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站立在海滨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你满面含笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见一丝伤痕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你浑身光华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像宝珠一样彩光照人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我幸福地投进你的怀抱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一寸土都那样熟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个人都那样亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海翻动着花的波浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高声地对我叙讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“远方来的朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是来作客呢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是重返故乡。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海啊，大连港，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是回家来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里曾住过我的爹娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大连啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我未到过的故乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的儿子虽是四处奔走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却只带着欢乐归来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一点儿悲伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为在我们亲爱的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处都像家乡一样。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}